data.description: Welcome to Glendales community. This home boasts numerous features and customizations surpassing newer constructions in the area. Upon entering, you are greeted by a high-ceiling foyer and a dining area perfect for creating lasting memories. The kitchen, with updated appliances, a new barn sink, extra shelving, and a floating shelf, opens to a living room and breakfast area, complete with a custom bench, ideal for hosting and unwinding. The owner’s suite is a retreat with a floating dresser, built-in safe, custom closet cabinets, and a bathroom with both a shower and separate tub for tranquil evenings. The second floor delights with a game room and spacious guest bedrooms.The garage enhanced with epoxy flooring and new shelvings. The sizable backyard is perfect for summer BBQ. Minutes away from 288, highway 6,fort bend toll road and beltway 8 for an easy access to the Medical center and many entertement and shoppings. Contact us today and make it your home !
